<p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">今天，是我国第12个</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">南京大屠杀死难者国家公祭日</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">88年前</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">侵华日军攻陷南京</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">制造了惨绝人寰、令人发指的大屠杀</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">88年过去了</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">我们不能忘！也不敢忘！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948219424.png" alt="1765948219424.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948219424.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">为缅怀南京大屠杀中惨遭杀戮的30万同胞，引导广大师生深刻铭记民族历史、厚植爱国主义情怀，汲取奋进力量，经济管理学院举办以“铭记历史，砥砺前行”为主题的国家公祭日主题活动。本次活动由师生党员、发展对象、各期入党积极分子及入团积极分子共同参加。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>主题班会，共忆山河记忆</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">各班级召开了“国殇铸魂，吾辈自强”主题班会。班会上，团支书带领同学们重温南京大屠杀的历史背景与关键史实，通过史料文献、幸存者口述片段等资料，让大家直观感受战争的残酷与和平的珍贵。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>国家公祭日</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948269655.png" alt="1765948269655.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948269655.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948285487.png" alt="1765948285487.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948285487.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>艺绘寄情，巧手定格祈愿</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">肌理画创作环节让同学们以艺术为媒传递祈愿。大家用画笔勾勒历史瞬间、描绘和平图景、书写青年担当。一幅幅色彩凝重而充满力量的作品，既是对死难同胞的缅怀，也是对和平生活的珍视。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948315277.png" alt="1765948315277.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948315277.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948333345.png" alt="1765948333345.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948333345.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">同时，同学们亲手折叠和平鸽，将对和平的向往融入每一个折痕，随后共同用和平鸽拼出“南京”字样，白色的鸽群在灯光下静静矗立，成为现场最庄重的纪念符号。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948360403.png" alt="1765948360403.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948360403.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948376361.png" alt="1765948376361.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948376361.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948388975.png" alt="1765948388975.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948388975.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>寄语签字，共抒赤子之心</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">师生们有序驻足在学院大厅的和平寄语墙前，大家手持笔具，郑重地签下自己的名字，一笔一划间，是对历史记忆的珍视，更是对守护和平、传承正义的坚定承诺。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">签名完毕，师生们纷纷拿起卡片，将心中对和平的向往、对祖国的祝福诉诸笔端。一句句真挚的留言贴满展板，汇聚成跨越时空的和平宣言。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948472059.png" alt="1765948472059.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948472059.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948522767.png" alt="1765948522767.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948522767.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948534335.png" alt="1765948534335.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948534335.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948545319.png" alt="1765948545319.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948545319.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948555085.png" alt="1765948555085.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948555085.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>默哀致哀，缅怀遇难同胞</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在经济管理学院一楼大厅，师生们皆沉浸于一片庄严肃静的氛围之中。全体人员肃立，默哀一分钟。秒针滴答作响，每一秒都承载着对死难同胞的深切缅怀，每一刻都传递着对历史的敬畏之心。没有喧嚣，没有言语，唯有无声的哀思在大厅中静静流淌，穿越时空，告慰着逝去的亡魂。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948591063.png" alt="1765948591063.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948591063.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948638734.png" alt="1765948638734.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948638734.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">默哀仪式后，经济管理学院学生第二党支部书记丁瑞风作为教师代表发言，结合历史事实讲述了南京大屠杀的惨痛教训，呼吁大家铭记苦难、珍惜和平，以实干担当践行青年使命；第34期入党积极分子胡子涵作为学生代表发言，分享了自己对历史的感悟与思考，表态将以青春之力传承红色基因。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948660832.png" alt="1765948660832.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948660832.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948688736.png" alt="1765948688736.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948688736.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>光影铸魂，感悟和平可贵</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">公祭仪式结束后，同学们共同观看历史影片《南京，南京》。镜头下，南京城的破碎山河、同胞的悲惨遭遇、仁人志士的英勇抗争，让在场每个人都深受震撼。观影过程中，大家热泪盈眶，更深刻地体会到“和平来之不易”的沉重内涵，进一步坚定了“铭记历史不是为了延续仇恨，而是为了守护和平”的认知。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948720604.png" alt="1765948720604.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948720604.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948741634.png" alt="1765948741634.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948741634.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948751458.png" alt="1765948751458.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948751458.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>宣讲赋能，凝聚奋进力量</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">最后，经济管理学院宣讲团负责人童梓盈结合详实的历史资料，讲述了南京大屠杀的历史真相与中华民族的抗争历程。她与同学们共勉：“作为新时代青年，我们既要铭记历史的伤痛，更要将悲痛转化为前行的动力，以史为鉴、脚踏实地，用知识武装头脑，用行动践行使命，为守护和平、振兴中华贡献青春力量。”</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948805717.png" alt="1765948805717.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948805717.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>结语</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">历史是最好的教科书，也是最好的清醒剂。三十万同胞的泣血呐喊，我们从未敢忘；和平年代的青春使命，我们矢志担当。本次国家公祭日主题活动，让每一位参与者都在铭记与缅怀中汲取奋进力量，在回望与前行中坚定理想信念。愿我们以史为鉴，不负韶华，用实干与担当守护这片山河无恙，用青春与热血书写民族复兴的崭新篇章。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948853346.png" alt="1765948853346.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1765948853346.png" style="width: 50%;"></p>